short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add MyTutor bookings to your calendar automatically.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically sync your MyTutor bookings to your Google Calendar, as soon as they are created.

Also provides enhancements for Tutors by improving payment transparency, showing you how much money you've made in a given time period, along with the amount you'll paid next payday.
